# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

- Documentation: translated build and README docs to English and updated them to reflect centralized versions (see `README.md`, `README-BUILD.md`, and `BUILD_VALIDATION_REPORT.md`).
- BOM and version management: dependency and plugin versions are centralized in the root `pom.xml` and a BOM is available at `bom/pom.xml` (artifact `com.prx:prx-commons-bom:0.0.1`).
- Build: default Java version set to 21 in the root `pom.xml`.
- Tests: prepared to add or update unit tests and test annotations (e.g., add `@DisplayName`) to meet coverage requirements.

## Version 0.0.1
- Updated dependencies.
- Added a class for secure SSL/HTTPS channel communication.
- Added `StandardException` class for capturing and propagating failures.
- Included authentication features.
